{"tid":2374216,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"京東方、Qualcomm 合作   推出全新 3D 超聲波指紋識別技術","createTime":"2021-01-21T05:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T16:22:32.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4b32711e2843787693951b5d37a25855d8a75d","tid":2374216,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"除了 Samsung 和 LG，京東方是其中一家能夠為 Apple 供應螢幕面板的生產商，早前有消息指京東方將會與 Qualcomm 合作，推出配備 Qualcomm 3D Sonic 感應器的一體化 OLED 柔性顯示解決方案，而這消息昨日已經獲得京東方證實。<br />\n<br />\n京東方透露他們與 Qualcomm 合作，開發全新集成 3D 超聲波指紋感應器的螢幕面板解決方案，而且已經開始量產。京東方和 Qualcomm 都不會自行發佈這項採用新技術的產品，但就會配合使用這柔性螢幕的客戶，透過新手機發佈時同步公開。<br />\n<br />\n3D 超聲波指紋技術擁有較高的安全度，它能夠產生 3D 指紋圖像，並且只有 3D 圖像方可以完成認證，又能夠分辨人類皮膚和其他物料，以減少假冒指紋進行破解。新技術還能夠穿透更厚的玻璃，以達到屏幕下識別的功能。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：cnbeta<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/217605/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F217605%2F1%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcLHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=5b2a915b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/217605/1/</a>"},{"pid":"e5e4094f4539dca6f058dbc03e28651d9c720bfa","tid":2374216,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"iPhone用京東方mon吹咗咁耐都仲未發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8865433c5835b4193914527b57e63b973bdb475","tid":2374216,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5e4094f4539dca6f058dbc03e28651d9c720bfa","tid":2374216,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"iPhone用京東方mon吹咗咁耐都仲未發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"都過唔到qc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}